event.title: ts inter 1st year results 2017
event.description:
TS inter 1st year results 2017 are about to release in 1st week of April 2017. manabadi com the leading educational website, along with government ts intermediate board will be releasing the results. http://ssc-results.org/ will release ts inter first year results with the courtesy of Board of Intermediate education Telangana state (biets) officially. Ts intermediate students can check their Telangana intermediate results in this page. Ts inter 1st year results 2017 are the 1st results of year released by any board of Telangana are officially released.
TS inter 2nd year results 2017According to the HRD government of India, all states of india has to provide +2 board exam marks, inter 2nd year board exam results to JEE (Joint entrance exam) board for IIT admissions and also to NEET (CBSE board) before the results of the respective entrance exams are release. This proposal has been accepted by tsbie or biets and in a press statement release by secretary of Telangana board of intermediate education the results of intermediate will be releasing in the month of April 2017 in dates of 20th to 22nd. As everyone aware before ts inter 2nd year results, ts inter 1st year results will be releasing. So we can expect the results in the month of April around 20thdate. Every year the ts inter first year results will be releasing in the first week of April. But this year we can expect a delay in the results release. However there is no guarantee whether it is in 1st, 2nd or 3rd week, but for your understanding the ts inter results 2017 are definite in the month of April. Keep watching this page for exact date of results.
